data.description: Introducing this charming Hurst residence nestled in the serene Shady Oaks neighborhood. This property, an ideal fixer-upper or perfect for first-time homebuyers looking to customize their dream home, offers boundless potential. With 1,434sf , this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom house presents a blank canvas for your creative vision. The spacious open concept layout provides ample room for transformation. The generous backyard is a versatile space for outdoor projects or relaxing in your own oasis. The desirable location in Shady Oaks offers a quiet, family-friendly atmosphere, while still being close to schools, shopping, and major thoroughfares. Embrace the opportunity to shape this house into your dream home. Don't miss out on this chance to turn your vision into reality!
